title: Xiang Ji
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Buffet, Take-out, Asian, Taiwanese, Singaporean
description: Restoran Sayur-Sayuran 香积素食 relocated here from previously being a stall at Plaza Sentosa. Emphasis is on mock meats but also serves vegetables. Offers a mixed of Asian cuisines, from breakfast and brunch to buffet and sandwiches.
